| `docs/PROGRAM_OVERVIEW.md` | Program status and milestones |
| `docs/DASHBOARD.md` | Current metrics |
| `docs/CONTEXT_INDEX.md` | Key people, channels, document index |
| `docs/GUIDELINES.md` | Team communication and process |
| `scripts/` | Automation scripts |

## What NOT to Do

- Do not start working without reading Memory Bank
- Do not end a session without updating Memory Bank and committing
- Do not force push
- Do not use emoji in headers or unicode bullets in documents
- Do not reference internal repo paths in external communications (Confluence, Jira, Slack)
- Do not store credentials in tracked files
- Do not overwrite another agent's session history
- Do not skip commits — if it is not committed, it can be lost
